text: avara mele vipattu eragidagalella avaru, o musa, ninna bali iruva avana (allahana) vagdanada adharadalli ninu nam'ma paravagi ninna odeyanannu prarthisu. Ondu vele ninu nam'ma melinda i vipattannu tolagisidare navu khandita ninnannu nambuvevu mattu isra'ilara santatiyannu ninna jote kaluhisikoduvevu, ennuttiddaru
